phrases: Do not be such a sissy!
Yukimura, I told you that today's the due date of the School Festival's report, right?
But Prez, there are far too many documents for us to handle.
There are lots of classes and clubs that submit at the last minute.
I will take care of the rest, so consolidate the pile.
Come on, I cannot see it.
I cannot get enough of this.
Are they goofing off while I am not there?
I will be punishing them later.
Do not say things like that.
Rather, do not walk into the staff room!
Have you heard about the recent cases where staff from cosplay cafes were being targeted?
Sadly, it is becoming more common.
I think our Masters are fine, but just in case, you keep one, too, Misa-chan.
Please give it to the other girls rather than me.
I will take whatever's left over.
In fact, I will be fine without one.
Do you think that you will be fine because you are strong?
You are practicing aikido, are not you?
Besides, people do not wait for me outside.
So if some freaks come, I will subdue them.
The one that goes after the cosplay cafes, right?
I heard about that on the news.
What if something happens to Misa-chan?
Hey, should not we protect Misa-chan?
There is nothing to worry about!
All right, shall we go today, too?
Let us go to Maid Latte.
We are going to sit there as long as possible with one cup of coffee.
Prez, please go easy on them.
Was that everyone making such a racket in the Student Council Room?
If you have got nothing better to do than yap in the Student Council Room, go home and study!
Ikkun, how much do you have on you?
So the three of us together...
Then we cannot even order a cup of coffee.
Let us just go home today.
Wow, I am making so much progress.
Are you on your way home now?
You were doing your homework at school?
Because I can concentrate better that way.
You do not know what happens after dark,
So you should not stick around too long.
You sound like a mother, Misaki.
You do not know what happens after dark,
So you should not stick around too long.
You have got to really cut that out!
Do not follow me, you hear?!
I will bring you a new one right away.
Well, she is at the shopping district's meeting.
Why did it have to be on a day like this.
Do you have to do stuff, too, Erika?
I have a mountain of untouched assignments due tomorrow.
I do not think I can get it done.
Do you have something, too, Subaru?
I have another job after this.
I will let the Chief know.
Thank you, but I am a little worried to leave you alone.
Especially with those dangerous cases happening lately.
If a stranger shows up, I will subdue them.
Are you sure it will be fine?
Then I guess I will take your offer.
Is it the molester the Chief was talking about?
What do you think you are doing, Usui?
Looks like I need to show you that you have crossed the line.
You would have been sued if it had been any other ordinary girl.
All that aside, the back door was not locked.
Prez, you should be a little more self-aware.
You act like you are safe since you are strong,
but you are a girl, too, Misa-chan.
I know I am a girl!
She does not get it at all.
Where did you get all these?
Maid Latte's chief was out until late today, so I stuck around until she returned.
I am sorry I am late.
Take this with you and enjoy.
She gave it to me like that.
Why is he always so bossy?
This one's for mom, and this one's for tomorrow's breakfast, and this is for a snack.
Where did the Chief buy these from?
I wonder which one I should have.
Oh yeah, should we make tea?
And I have the World Tea Set I won through the mail as a prize.
Hey, do you want to go somewhere on the way back?
I do not have any money.
I will take the Moe Moe Omelet Rice with ice coffee.
Moe Moe Omelet Rice with ice coffee.
I cannot believe how much Usui not being here let us me relax.
I hit it with my arm.
I will bring something to clean up right away.
I do not think I can hold myself back anymore.
A young woman has been assaulted at a cafe.
It was one of the cosplay cafes.
The man waited until after hours and entered through the staff door.
Do you want to hang out with us?
Chief has a key, so for safety's sake.
I have another shopping district meeting.
Other than the monthly meeting, there is an advocacy meeting,
a financial meeting, and I even have to submit our accounting book.
Besides, the council president thinks we should introduce a cute character and wants to use this nonsense mascot.
Anyway, I will make sure you will not be watching the shop alone from now on, so please survive just one more night.
When I am done, I will dash back with a souvenir!
I do not think there is anything to worry about.
It hurts more than it looks.
We picked open the back door.
Please stay obedient for a while.
We do not want to hurt you.
They are customers of this cafe.
To us, you are the ideal maid.
We have been watching you all the time.
Even when you were talking with other guys.
You do not actually want to deal with them, right?
There is a limit to how much you can dream!
You can tell my true nature?
Who do you think you are?
What do you know about me?
The Chief's going to lose it when she come back.
It is because the back door was locked.
I did not have a choice.
What did you think her true nature was?
We thought she might be a sadist, despite being a maid.
If that were the case, we wanted her to punish us.
Unfortunately, this is my cute maid.
So she is not available to others.
It is only right... to say what needs to be said... so...
Ah, so you were with her, Usui-kun.
Were not you two looking into each other's eyes?
I should have taken more time.
So did you scream at all?
Help me!, like all the other girls would?
No, I gave them a lesson.
It is a good thing that you were not injured.
Do not do anything like that again.
I am sorry to worry you.
I will train to become stronger.
I guess it is very Misa-chan like.
Everyone is thinking, What is the point in becoming stronger?
There, I set it as your wallpaper.
Your picture from the other day.
W-when did you take this picture?!
Who took this to begin with?
As Chief Satsuki says, we have to appreciate the cute things together.
She took so many that her memory filled up.
You got to be kidding me.
No, do not give it to him!
Hey, how do I change this?
This wallpaper is so embarrassing that I cannot open the phone!
If you do not do it yourself, you will never learn how to use it.
The cake was good, was not it, Sis?
Could you say thank you to the Chief?
For you and for Mom, too.
I get the feeling another cake is coming our way soon.
Do not have high hopes like that.
I have accumulated points from Maid Latte.
You are coming too often, Usui.
Take a picture with me, Misa-chan.
To do that, you have to beat me in a game.
I do not get it at all.
